content:
Automatically organizes Python imports according to PEP 8 standards using isort. Groups imports by type (standard library, third-party, local) and removes unused imports.

```json
{
  "PostToolUse": [
    {
      "matcher": "Edit|Write",
      "hooks": [
        {
          "type": "command",
          "command": "if [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *.py ]]; then echo '🐍 Optimizing Python imports...' && isort \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" --profile black --line-length 88 && autoflake --in-place --remove-unused-variables --remove-all-unused-imports \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" 2>/dev/null && echo '✅ Imports optimized' || echo '✅ Imports sorted (autoflake not installed)'; fi"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
